---
title: Korean-Style Bulgogi Kimbap Casserole with Roasted Seaweed, Pickled Veggies, Spicy Mayo & Sesame Seeds
description: This dish, perfect for sharing, is inspired by kimbap, a Korean staple dish of protein and vegetables rolled up in seasoned rice and seaweed sheets. We’ve serving the components—bulgogi-style beef, tender carrots and spinach, and sesame rice—casserole-style, topped with pickled radishes and cucumber, spicy mayo, and toasted seaweed. Ready to dig in?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67f394ce27b8e5819ffeba49-c12b7891.jpeg
